DBIx::SQSHRC

Connect to the database using DBI and the user's .sqshrc file.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc DBIx::SQSHRC

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=DBIx-SQSHRC

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/DBIx-SQSHRC

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/DBIx-SQSHRC

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/DBIx-SQSHRC/


